name: My Love You Are Floating Away
description: For this NFT, to be a true "owner" you must watch this stop motion animation 11 times and then go for an 11 minute walk. You should only think about what you see on your walk and DO NOT LOOK AT ANY DEVICE while you are on your walk.  Once you are done with your walk go back and watch video as many times as you like and when you are ready say out loud "I Own You Sucker"
